'From Squeak 2.6alpha of August 6, 1999 on 27 September 1999 at 8:54:14 am'!"Change Set:		CcgStepFix-bfDate:			27 September 1999Author:			Bert FreudenbergFixes a walkback when simulating the new compiled primitive stuff, and a typo in one example"!!FlippyArrayPlugin2 methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'bf 9/24/1999 14:39'!primReverse	| rcvr t a b |	rcvr _ self 		primitive:	'primReverse'		parameters:	#()		receiver:	#Array.	a _ 0. b _ rcvr size - 1.	[a < b] whileTrue:		[t _ rcvr at: a.		 rcvr at: a put: (rcvr at: b).		 rcvr at: b put: t.		 a _ a + 1. b _ b - 1].	^rcvr asOop: Array! !!TestCodeGenerator methodsFor: 'C linkage new' stamp: 'bf 9/24/1999 14:53'!ccgValBlock: valString	^[:index | String streamContents:		[:aStream | aStream			nextPutAll: 'interpreterProxy success: (interpreterProxy ';			nextPutAll: valString;			nextPutAll: ': (interpreterProxy stackValue: ';			nextPutAll: index asString;			nextPutAll: '))']] fixTemps! !